These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, gardening, hiking
City: hamburg, berlin, venice
3 different games are played: chess, backgammon, poker
3 different pets are kept: lizard, rabbit, hedgehog
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, zinnia, amaryllis
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, snowmobile
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, davidoff, bolivar
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is the person playing poker##1
 2. the person playing poker is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person playing backgammon##1
 4. the person driving the boat is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
 5. the alhambra-smoker is the owner of the rabbit##1
 6. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 7. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 8. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 9. the person traveling to berlin is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
10. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby      | skydiving  | gardening   | hiking      |
| City          | venice      | hamburg     | berlin     |
| Game           | backgammon | poker  | chess   |
| Pet   | rabbit   | hedgehog     | lizard  |
| Flower   | balloon-flower      | zinnia      | amaryllis      |
| Transport   | snowmobile      | jet-ski    | boat   |
| Cigar         | alhambra    | davidoff | bolivar |

