.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-2::.
3 different games are played: bridge, domino, backgammon
There 3 different types of food: kale, cucumber, raspberry
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, black, coral
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, july, august
City: new-york, rome, colone
House: townhouse, farmhouse, ranch-style
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, bluemaster, cain
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is in the middle##1
 2. the person playing backgammon is the townhouse house##1
 3. the bluemaster-smoker is in the middle##1
 4. the person playing domino is the person traveling to colone##1
 5. the person eating kale is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 7. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1
 8. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
 9. the cain-smoker is on the far left##1
10. the person eating raspberry is the person traveling to new-york##1
11. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person who likes pink##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Game         | domino | backgammon  | bridge     |
| Food           | kale        | cucumber | raspberry    |
| Color   | black  | coral    | pink    |
| Birthday   | august    | july    | june   |
| City           | colone        | rome    | new-york        |
| House         | farmhouse     | townhouse  | ranch-style     |
| Cigar     | cain         | bluemaster       | tiparillo |

