3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, bolivar, game
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, august, december
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, baking, hiking
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 2. the person who likes white is on the far left##1
 3. the person who likes brown is on the right of the victorian house##1
 4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 5. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
 6. the person who likes white is the modern house##1
 7. the person who growstulip is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
10. the person who growsaconite is the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| House      | modern   | victorian         | art-deco |
| Game          | monopoly  | billiard        | snooker    |
