House: craftsman, tower, colonial
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, airplane, subway
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, iced-tea
 1. the doctor is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
 2. the person who growsorchid is on the far right##1
 3. the colonial house is the person who growsbellflower##1
 4. the analyst is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 5. the police-officer is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 6. the police-officer is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is in the middle##1
 8. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is the tower house##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
11. the person who likes azure is on the far right##1
12. the analyst is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3       |
