.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-17::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, ship, taxi
City: san-francisco, paris, hamburg
House: modern, wooden, victorian
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, vegafina, siglo
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, may, december
3 different pets are kept: snake, hedgehog, horse
3 different games are played: go, poker, chess
 1. the victorian house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 2. the vegafina-smoker is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 3. the person driving the taxi is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 4. the person playing go is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 6. the wooden house is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 7. the person playing poker is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 8. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
10. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
11. the game-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |       3        |
| Transport      | taxi   | car        | ship           |
| City         | san-francisco | hamburg          | paris      |
| House           | modern   | wooden | victorian |
| Cigar   | vegafina  | game       | siglo         |
| Birthday   | may    | december          | february        |
| Pet   | hedgehog  | horse        | snake     |
| Game         | go   | chess         | poker       |

