.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-18::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, december, march
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, jazz, hip-hop
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, white, brown
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, havana, alhambra
3 different pets are kept: snake, goat, dog
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, marigold, poppy
House: victorian, art-deco, tower
 1. the art-deco house is the person who likes white##1
 2. the person who growsmarigold is the person who likes white##1
 3. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 4. the fan of electronic is on the far right##1
 5. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the tower house##1
 6. the person who likes brown is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
 8. the owner of the snake is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 9. the blend-smoker is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is the owner of the dog##1
11. the blend-smoker is on the left of the victorian house##1
12. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |      3      |
| Birthday      | august       | march      | december      |
| Music-Genre          | jazz        | hip-hop | electronic   |
| Color         | brown       | white    | emerald  |
