.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-19::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, electrician, manager
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, video-games, sudoku
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, january, may
There are 3 different favourite colors: orange, chestnut, mauve
3 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, bridge
House: colonial, victorian, tower
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, old-henry, oliveros
 1. the dunhill-smoker is on the far right##1
 2. the manager is in the middle##1
 3. the colonial house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 4. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 5. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1
 7. the person playing bridge is the victorian house##1
 8. the person playing bridge is on the left of the musician##1
 9. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
10. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Job      | electrician      | manager         | musician |
| Hobby          | video-games | sudoku        | card-games   |
| Birthday   | february | january       | may   |
| Color   | orange   | mauve          | chestnut       |
| Game   | backgammon  | bridge      | canasta   |
| House           | tower    | victorian        | colonial        |
| Cigar         | oliveros  | old-henry | dunhill     |

