.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-20::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, volleyball, sailing
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, bluemaster, chaman
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, february, april
City: edinburgh, miami, boston
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, begonia, iris
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, chestnut, blue
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, scooter, helicopter
 1. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
 3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
 4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 5. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who likes emerald##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is the person who likes emerald##1
 8. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
 9. the person who growsiris is in the middle##1
10. the person driving the helicopter is in the middle##1
11. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3      |
| Sport      | volleyball       | climbing     | sailing         |
| Cigar          | bluemaster      | oliveros  | chaman     |
| Birthday         | june | february     | april |
| City   | edinburgh  | boston | miami     |
| Flower   | sunflower    | iris      | begonia     |
| Color   | chestnut  | blue    | emerald  |
| Transport           | taxi   | helicopter      | scooter      |

 